{
  "name": "RPlog_Fourth_Battle_of_Corellia",
  "title": "The Fourth Battle of Corellia",
  "summary": "The Empire springs an elaborate trap on Corellia: a damaged freighter, the Angel Dust, lures the New Republic and CorSec defenders into the open before detonating an EMP weapon that plunges the entire system and planet into total darkness, killing power to every ship, weapon, and comlink. Under Admiral Drayson Honos and Admiral Danik Kreldin, the massive Imperial fleet jumps in and pours walkers, dropships, and troops onto the helpless world, demanding surrender by white flag. Amid the chaos, the Jedi pilot Johanna crash-lands her EMP-killed X-wing into a lingerie shop, is found by her mentor Jessalyn, and joins the doomed resistance led by Marine Colonel Sabrina Rheatis, who scrambles to arm civilians with shielded weapons. As Storm Commandos under Sergeant Rob, Scimitar bombers under Darenak Alesis, AT-ATs, and the crimson Royal Guard under Tribune Korolov grind the defenders down, Johanna's Sith brother Warlord Malign hunts her through the dark streets and corners her alley. Despite fierce guerrilla resistance, Corellia falls; Sabrina orders her men to flee to safety and is finally stunned and captured, leaving the world conquered.",
